# Starting page
url https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/

Registration form on the starting page:    .//form[@id='registration-form']
Username field:                            .//input [@id='username-register']
Email field:                               .//input [@id='email-register']
Password field:                            .//input [@id='password-register']
Submit button:                             .//button[@type='submit']
Button contains text 'Sign up for OurApp': .//button [text()='Sign up for OurApp']
Registration form 'Sing in' in the header: .//form[@action='/login']
Username field in the header:              .//form[@action='/login']//input[@name='username']
Password field in the header:              .//input [@type='hidden' and @name='_csrf']
Sign In button in the header:              .//button[contains(text(),'Sign In')]

# Home page of the logged in user
https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/
 has Xpath locator .//html [@class='fontawesome-i2svg-active fontawesome-i2svg-complete'] contains numbers!!!

Sign out button:                           .//button
Create Post button:                        .//a[@href='/create-post']

# Create Post page
https://qa-complex-app-for-testing.herokuapp.com/create-post
Title field:                                 .//input[@id='post-title']
Body Content text box:                       .//textarea[@id='post-body']
Check box "This is unique post":             .//input[@id='”UniquePost”']
Drop-down list with types of post (public):  .//select//option[@value='All Users']
Drop-down list with types of post (private): .//select//option[@value='One Person']
Button "Save New Post":                      .//button[contains(text(),'Save New Post')]